text: It Just Comes Natural is the 24th studio album by George Strait. The album was released on October 3, 2006 through MCA Nashville Records. The song "Give It Away" from the album was Strait's 41st Number One for Billboard Hot Country Songs. ==Chart positions== Chart (2006) Peak position U.S. Billboard Top Country Albums 1 U.S. Billboard 200 3 ==References== Category:2006 albums Category:Country albums
